      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is gone. the crash hit harder than anyone expected and the debt is just... it's insurmountable. i lost the company, the house, everything. i can't even imagine walking back into my parents' house or looking my wife in the eye. i'm just a complete failure. there's no coming back from this.",
